%% Diagram: Transport Decision Tree
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[Need real-time sync] --> B{Bidirectional?}

    B -->|server to client only| D{HTTP/2 or HTTP/3?}
    D -->|Yes| E[SSE]
    D -->|No / restricted proxy| F[SSE + HTTP/1.1 fallback]
    E --> EU{Client uplink?}
    F --> EU
    EU -->|Yes, infrequent| G[SSE + HTTP POST]
    EU -->|No| H[SSE only]

    B -->|both directions| I{Greenfield, Chromium-leading OK?}
    I -->|Yes| J[WebTransport / HTTP/3]
    I -->|No, need parity| K[WebSocket]

    J --> L{Offline support?}
    K --> L
    L -->|Yes| M[Add IndexedDB queue + reconnect with replay]
    L -->|No| N[Connection manager + heartbeats]

    K -.->|blocked by enterprise proxy| P[Long polling fallback]
